  "description": "Catalog of land cover, land change, rangeland vegetation component, and related remote-sensing products produced and distributed by the Multi-Resolution Land Characteristics (MRLC) Consortium for the United States and North America. Includes Annual NLCD, RCMAP, Exotic Annual Grass products, NALCMS, and legacy NLCD products, with access via direct downloads, interactive tools, and OGC web services.",
